{"tid":779143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警 方 聲 稱 陳 家 駒 一 人 阻 街, 強 行 帶 走","createTime":"2018-08-14T08:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T02:31:26.000Z","uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bea689462548263852a12224b0bdb74900a26afe","tid":779143,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2162288594050511&amp;id=2048175568795148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2162288594050511%26id%3D2048175568795148&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3307f0b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2162288594050511&amp;id=2048175568795148</a><br />\n<br />\n［警方禁止示威者於外國記者協會門外聚集］<br />\n<br />\n11:50 支持言論自由人士到達，但被警方趕到雲咸大廈外，另設示威區，當中有人被抬離現場，FCC門外只剩反港獨人士<br />\n<br />\n12:04 警方聲稱本組織召集人陳家駒一人停留已構成阻街，繼而被四名警員強硬抬走，至東耀商業大廈門外<br />\n<br />\n12:06 六名警員包圍本組織成員，並推至牆角，稱空間不足，不準停留<br />\n<br />\n12:20 記者繼續了解情形，市民相繼到場<br />\n<br />\n12:40 部份示威者成功回到FCC牆外，警方設置鐵馬<br />\n<br />\n14:00 到場人士仍留守FCC牆外示威區<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fcchk.org/videos/321168738655457/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffcchk.org%2Fvideos%2F321168738655457%2F&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b9b535c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fcchk.org/videos/321168738655457/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=529107497535329&amp;id=710476795704610&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D529107497535329%26id%3D710476795704610%26_rdr&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e7c791b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=529107497535329&amp;id=710476795704610&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/videos/live/m/redirect/297751830998486/?_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fvideos%2Flive%2Fm%2Fredirect%2F297751830998486%2F%3F_rdr&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=57b732ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/videos/live/m/redirect/297751830998486/?_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2169552379953127&amp;id=1658518877723149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2169552379953127%26id%3D1658518877723149&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=526500be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2169552379953127&amp;id=1658518877723149</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1058912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1058912&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c3e81b0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1058912&h=2fbfd0ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1058912</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=582165735518865&amp;id=366243453719070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D582165735518865%26id%3D366243453719070&d=7%2FGlMB%2F%2B1qOC0kvt7OfS3JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1a2f3062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=582165735518865&amp;id=366243453719070</a>"},{"pid":"46e8fd5d3ddbfc6e5f2a9fa4914e3b858fc7f46e","tid":779143,"uid":143499,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"關sir好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8e9f19f6ee6e58f4a6cc0e843115800039fdc1","tid":77914